Output docs/v4-phase2-narrow-phosphor.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 700
Set TypingSpeed 15ms

Type "stty cols 72 rows 30; ORC_HOME=/tmp/orc-vhs-phase2-narrow env -u NO_COLOR rust/target/release/pi-orchestra --theme phosphor home"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "n"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+g
Type "z"
Sleep 2s
Ctrl+g
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
